{
  "stem": "13471.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Admiral Wilkinson was the admiral to whom I report every morning.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when I first put in my request for sea duty, I had mentioned this to Admiral Wilkinson in one of these morning get-togethers.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he, being a seagoing man, approved.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He says, fine, I think it's a good idea.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He says, I'll approve.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so when my application got over to BUPERS, where my friends, you see, where the underlings were, there was a long-hand, written endorsement on the bottom of my request-- a favorable endorsement signed by Admiral Wilkinson.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so what happened-- another superior of mine realized that if I left, he'd have to find somebody else that spoke German.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that was too much trouble.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So he took a pair of scissors, and he snipped off the admiral's [LAUGHS] endorsement.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But he didn't snip too good, and a part of the upper line was left on the original.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so in my file today, in the Navy Department, is this short, skirted letter with a few-- anyway, so I say, what the hell am I going to do?",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then my friends, you know, were in the-- in the BUPERS.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And well, finally they said they didn't get enough people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They're going to put it out again.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I said, great.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I said, how about putting it through this time?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so they did.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the second time around, I made it in.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And-- And where were you posted?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To-- [LAUGHS] you ever hear of the 90-Day Wonders?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All right.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
